# Dastyare Social CS

Next.js 16 creator studio. REST API at `/api`, docs at `/docs`, OpenAPI at `/openapi.json`.

## Key paths

- API routes: `src/app/api/`
- Business logic: `src/lib/api/`
- DB schema: `src/lib/db/schema/`
- Auth: `src/lib/auth/`
- Config: `config/app.config.yml` (source) → `config/app.config.json` (generated)

## Rules

- Minimal diffs; do not refactor unrelated code
- Keep API logic in `src/lib/api/`, routes stay thin
- Use `@/` imports, existing Zod/drizzle-zod schemas
- After API changes: add JSDoc `@openapi` tags, run `bun run openapi:generate`
- Never commit secrets (.env, S3 keys, auth secrets)
- Read AGENTS.md for API details before integration work
